<chapter line="1">Pāṭihāriyadīpanīgāthā</chapter>
<hangnum line="2" number="175"></hangnum>
<gatha1 line="3">Brahmassa saddaṃ karavīkabhāṇiṃ,</gatha1>
<gatha2 line="4">Yathicchitaṃ sāvayituṃ samatthaṃ;</gatha2>
<gatha3 line="5">Saccaṃ piyaṃ bhūtahitaṃ vadantaṃ,</gatha3>
<gathalast line="6">Na pūjaye ko hi naro sacetano.</gathalast>
<hangnum line="7" number="176"></hangnum>
<gatha1 line="8">Iddhi ca ādesanānusāsanī,</gatha1>
<gatha2 line="9">Pāṭihīre bhagavā vasī ahu;</gatha2>
<gatha3 line="10">Katvāna accherasupāṭihīraṃ,</gatha3>
<gathalast line="11">Desesi dhammaṃ anukampimaṃ pajaṃ.</gathalast>
